2014年9月26日，[[美国|美国]][[爱荷华州|爱荷华州]][[艾奥瓦城_(艾奥瓦州)|爱荷华市]]警方在一辆市郊公寓外停放的车辆的后备箱内发现一具尸体。其后警方认定死者是来自中国的20岁女留学生'''邵童'''<ref name="Sino-US story">{{cite news|authors=Zhang Han, Wang Lingyu and Zhong Ying|title=In-depth: Uncovering truth behind murder of Chinese student in US|url=http://www.sino-us.com/10/In-depth-Uncovering-truth-behind-murder-of-Chinese-student-in-US.html|newspaper=Sino-US.com|date=April 14, 2015|accessdate=August 16, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065750/http://www.sino-us.com/10/In-depth-Uncovering-truth-behind-murder-of-Chinese-student-in-US.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，其生前就读于[[爱荷华州立大学|爱荷华州立大学]]（Iowa State University），而案发车辆也正由她的名义所注册。她此前曾被报告称其已经失踪9天<ref name="Gazzette warrant unseal story">{{cite news|last=Hermiston|first=Lee|title=Warrants reveal details in investigation of Tong Shao's Iowa City death|url=http://thegazette.com/subject/news/public-safety/crime/warrant-li-overheard-shao-talking-about-him-with-other-man-booked-flight-two-days-before-emergency-20150108|newspaper=The Gazette|location=Cedar Rapids, IA|date=January 7, 2015|accessdate=August 16, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307194318/http://www.thegazette.com/subject/news/public-safety/crime/warrant-li-overheard-shao-talking-about-him-with-other-man-booked-flight-two-days-before-emergency-20150108|dead-url=no}}</ref>。死因被认定为[[窒息|窒息]]致死的[[他杀|他杀]]<ref name="Press-Citizen story">{{cite news|last=berg|first=Zach|title=Death of former ISU student found dead in IC ruled a homicide|url=http://www.press-citizen.com/story/news/crime-and-courts/2015/01/09/tong-shao-death-ruled-homicide/21524791/|newspaper=Iowa City Press-Citizen|date=January 9, 2015|accessdate=August 16, 2015}}</ref>。

邵童最后一次露面是9月7日在位于名为内华达市的小镇外的一家宾馆，地处爱荷华州立大学所在地[[艾姆斯|艾姆斯]]以东。她事前曾与她就读于位于爱荷华市的爱荷华大学（University of Iowa）的男友李向南共度周末。根據報導，她的豐田凱美瑞车辆和尸体即在李向南所住的公寓小区内被发现<ref name="Press-Citizen story 2">{{cite news|last=berg|first=Zach|title=Tong Shao stayed in hotel with boyfriend days before going missing|url=http://www.press-citizen.com/story/news/crime-and-courts/2015/01/16/tong-shao-warrant-reveals-iowa-hotel-xiangnan-li-going-missing/21876321/|newspaper=Iowa City Press-Citizen|date=January 16, 2015|accessdate=August 16, 2015}}</ref>。事件暴露时李已經搭機回國，并不在场。警方相信在案发第二天一早匆促退房后，他用死者的手机以她的口吻给她的朋友发短信称她要出行一段时间，并同时称李因为家中急事已返回中国。9月8日，李向南登机经芝加哥中转，并在9月10日到达中国，隨後廣州、長安等地逃亡。於是2015年年初，爱荷华州[[約翰遜縣_(愛阿華州)|约翰逊县]]官方指控李向南犯有一级谋杀罪并发出[[逮捕令|逮捕令]]。中国部分网民开始转发仍然在逃的李向南的照片和信息，兩人在前往美國之前的關係也被傳開，後來李亦在法庭上做出有關口供。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.backchina.com/news/2016/03/30/418231.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-01 |archive-date=2016-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201211807/http://www.backchina.com/news/2016/03/30/418231.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据中国法律规定，中国公民在境外犯罪，中国拥有管辖权，且不会引渡本国公民<ref name="Ames Tribune arrest story">{{cite news|last=Aronsen|first=Gavin|title=ISU student's suspected killer apprehended in China|url=http://amestrib.com/news/isu-student-s-suspected-killer-apprehended-china|newspaper=Ames Tribune|date=July 2, 2015|accessdate=August 16, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727160630/http://amestrib.com/news/isu-student-s-suspected-killer-apprehended-china|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在中国浙江警方赴美国搜集证据后，亦对李向南提出指控。2015年5月，李向南向温州警方投案。

2016年3月23日温州市中级人民法院开庭审理该案。2016年6月22日，温州市中级人民法院公开宣判，被告人犯故意杀人罪，判处无期徒刑，剥夺政治权利终身。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.wzfy.gov.cn/system/2016/06/22/012394776.shtml|title=中国留美女大学生被杀案今日宣判 - 温州法院网|accessdate=2016-06-23|work=www.wzfy.gov.cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918180444/http://www.wzfy.gov.cn/system/2016/06/22/012394776.shtml|archive-date=2016-09-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

